textAnnotations.description:
"MUMMY, I HEARD DDDY
SAY REPUBLICANS ARE
CUTTING $13 BILLION IN
AID TO THE POOR
WONT THAT HURT POOR
PEOPLE WHO GOT HIT
B THAT HURRICANE?"
"No, SWEETIE, IT'S LIKE
BARBARA BUSH SAD
THEY'RE ALL MUCH BETTER
OFF NOW THAT THBY'RE
LIVING IN A STADIUM!"
